A CDN allows for the quick transfer of assets needed for loading Internet content including HTML pages, javascript files, stylesheets, images, and videos 
it cache content at the network edge, which improves web application performance

a cdn is network of servers linked together to deliver content faster.inorder to improve speed and connectivity CDN will be placed at axchange point of ISPs this is called IXP ( Internet exchange points ). at IXP these ISP talks to different networks 




